  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add cumin seeds and let them sizzle.",
    "Add chopped onion, minced garlic, and grated ginger. Cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add chopped green chili and cook for another minute.",
    "Add mulukhiyah leaves and cook until they wilt.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together coconut milk, coriander powder, turmeric powder, and salt.",
    "Pour the coconut milk mixture into the pan and stir well.",
    "Transfer the curry to a sous-vide bag and seal.",
    "Cook in a water bath at 180°F (82°C) for 30 minutes.",
    "Serve hot over rice or with roti."
